@startuml
title clip -> action -> state -> task 層図

left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName Yu Gothic UI
skinparam defaultFontSize 18
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 24
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #f7fbff
  FontColor black
}
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ranksep 20
skinparam nodesep 20

rectangle "clip\n元の animation data" as Clip
rectangle "action\n使う区間を切り出す" as Action
rectangle "state\n今どの action を選ぶか" as State
rectangle "schedule / task\n時間進行と補間実行" as Task
rectangle "node pose\nupdate" as NodePose

Clip --> Action
Action --> State
State --> Task
Task --> NodePose

note bottom of Clip
アセットが持つ連続データ
end note

note bottom of Action
どこを使うかを決める
end note

note bottom of State
状況に応じて選択する
end note

note bottom of Task
実際に時間を進める
end note
@enduml
